OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and sunny once low cloud,
OL,6,Fmist and patchy fog clears, although
OL,7,Fsometimes the sunshine will be hazy.
OL,8,FAnother warm day for inland areas,
OL,9,Fwhile the coast remains cooler with an
OL,10,Fonshore breeze and perhaps further
OL,11,Fmist and low cloud.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLargely clear initially then
OL,14,Fmist and low cloud is expected to
OL,15,Fspread westwards. There is a chance of
OL,16,Fa slight frost, and patchy fog, for
OL,17,Fany places that remain clear.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,168,160,301,260,100,100
