PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F167A1777093520
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FEarly mist, patchy fog or low
OL,6,Fcloud will disperse leaving sunny
OL,7,Fconditions before cloud increases.
OL,8,FRather warm for many places, except
OL,9,Fcooler across eastern Lincolnshire,
OL,10,Fespecially along the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fbright spells and scattered heavy
OL,14,Fshowers developing. Tuesday and
OL,15,FWednesday dry with bright or sunny
OL,16,Fspells, but perhaps coastal low cloud
OL,17,Ffor Tuesday. Temperatures generally
OL,18,Fnear average inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
